                SELECT 1
                from EBA_QPOLL_POLLS p,
                     eba_qpoll_results r
                where p.id = r.poll_id
                  and p.status_id = 3 
                  and ((p.anonymous_yn = 'Y' and r.APEX_SESSION_ID = :APP_SESSION) or
                       r.apex_user = :APP_USER) 
                  and nvl(r.is_valid_yn,'Y') = 'N'
                ```
